<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(بأَش)</span> : باءَشَهُ: امْتَنعَ منه.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(بغل)</span> البُغْلُول: الغَوْطُ من الرَّمْلِ، وهو يُنْبِتُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(بزو)</span> : الإِبْزاءُ: الإِرْضاعُ،<span class="c5"> وهذا بَزِيِّي:</span> أَي رَضِيعِي.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(بصر)</span> : ثَوْبٌ مُبْصِرٌ: أَي وَسَطٌ، وكذلك رَجُلٌ مُبْصِرُ النُّطْق والمِشْيَةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(بطح)</span> : هذه بُطْحَةُ صِدْق: أي خَصْلَةُ صِدْق.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(برم)</span> : البرَمَةُ: العَظَايَةً.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(بجم)</span> : بَجمَ قَرْنُه بُجُوماً: طَلَع.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(بحزج)</span> : البَجْرَج: القَصِير العَظِيمُ البَطْنِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>والبَكْرُ يُسمَّى البَجْرَجَ، لِعظَم بَطْنِه.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>